title: PartialRow
description: Represents a single partial row of a TableEntity.

rowId.description: The immutable ID of a row.

values.description: The values for columns of this row as a map. The key is the columnId and value is the cell value. To perform updates on a row inside of Views, a pair of {"key":"etag", "value":"REPLACE-WITH-ETAG-OF-ENTITY-BEING-UPDATED"} must be also included.
